overview.en: As the first matchmaking exchange platform of 100sunEX, Token is obtained by mining with PSS algorithm as a token of value and rights. In the later decentralized DEX, it will be used as the parent currency for Multi Chain cross chain, and will be connected to DeFi, Gamefi, Metaverse and other fields in the future to realize its long-term value.
overview.zh: 作为 100SunEX 首家撮合型交易所平台通证，采用 PSS 算法挖矿获得，作为早期平台的价值和权益 的令牌，将在后期完成去中心化 DEX 转型时作为母币进行多链的跨链和映射，并将在未来生态接入 DeFi、GameFi 等领域，实现其长期价值。
